001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.models;
002
003import java.util.Objects;
004
005/**
006 * Used by ControlIQSleepScheduleResponse and RemindersResponse.Reminder
007 */
008public class MinsTime {
009    private final int hour;
010    private final int min;
011
012    public MinsTime(int totalMins) {
013        this.hour = totalMins / 60;
014        this.min = totalMins % 60;
015    }
016
017    public MinsTime(int hour, int min) {
018        this.hour = hour;
019        this.min = min;
020    }
021
022    public int hour() {
023        return hour;
024    }
025
026    public int min() {
027        return min;
028    }
029
030    public int encode() {
031        return hour*60 + min;
032    }
033
034    @Override
035    public boolean equals(Object o) {
036        if (this == o) return true;
037        if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass()) return false;
038        MinsTime minsTime = (MinsTime) o;
039        return encode() == minsTime.encode();
040    }
041
042    @Override
043    public int hashCode() {
044        return Objects.hash(hour, min);
045    }
046}
